{"tid":362311,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"齊探討一個男人要幾強 先肯食軟糖？","createTime":"2017-08-16T22:54:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-17T00:11:05.000Z","uid":4662,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"46f7119936fad30e27dc4b332319be743d837706","tid":362311,"uid":4662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T22:54:23.000Z","msg":"張繼聰為左脱離外界覺得佢靠老婆 kay <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n食軟飯<br />\n見得到佢好努力改變<br />\n令好多網民都睇得出佢<br />\n自己都係有實力既<br />\n口才好<br />\n搞笑<br />\n有型<br />\n<br />\n究竟大奶奶一個男人<br />\n竟然要食軟糖<br />\n生小朋友唔係由心愛錫<br />\n係當佢地賺錢工具<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 寧願靠自己努力絕不吃軟糖<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食軟糖冇罪 有得食唔食 罪大惡極<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">網民某程度上先係佢地成家既老闆</span></span>"},{"pid":"2fb9a0bf3742748d4707374b2722c7f71b24187f","tid":362311,"uid":88829,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T23:11:41.000Z","msg":"食軟糖 有咩所謂<br />\n最緊要有得食"},{"pid":"50bad71b9652236d8c628bbb615f16d3a29a475a","tid":362311,"uid":4662,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T23:41:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食軟糖 有咩所謂<br />\n最緊要有得食</blockquote><br />\n負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f65104c7da380097dd19257df3ca120e72fc387","tid":362311,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T23:45:27.000Z","msg":"軟糖我都食開"},{"pid":"6816ee196e0902d5411bf9290a07103e902f2a6e","tid":362311,"uid":4662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T23:46:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>軟糖我都食開</blockquote><br />\n邊種軟糖先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccde5490bd2d64a93aa845920f6a0f44f0998ad3","tid":362311,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T00:10:17.000Z","msg":"